MBOMBELA – All customers had a chance to win – all they had to do was buy at the butchery, fill in the details including their telephone number and put their entries into a box placed inside the shop. Entries for the competition were open right up until close of business on Friday April 6. The draw took place on Saturday April 7. Nelson Calaca. Khoza was among 10 lucky winners, whose numbers were called during the live draw. The finalists were asked to pick a box, out of 10 only one had a key, nine were empty. Khoza was speechless when she opened a little black box with the key inside.